    <div class="card bg-light mb-3" style="max-width: 58rem;">
        
        <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">Brief Itinerary</h4>
          <br>
          
          <h5 class="card-title"> Day 0</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            <ul>
              <li>Pick up from Bangalore by 8:30 PM (approx)</li>
            </ul>
            <br>
          </p>
          <h5 class="card-title"> Day 1 – Saturday</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            <ul>
              
              <li>Reach Wayanad around 7:30 am ( approx )</li>
              <li>Freshen Up & have Breakfast</li>
              <li>Short Hike to Arnamala View Point</li>
              <li>River-stream trek and relax by the river</li>
              <li>Lunch at the campsite</li>
              <li>Drive down to Ambukuthi Campsite</li>
              <li>Dinner and Bonfire ( if weather permits 0</li>
              <li>Night trek to Ambukuthi Hills</li>
              <li>Pitch your tents and camp on the hill overnight</li>
            </ul>
            <br>
          </p>

          <h5 class="card-title"> Day 2 – Sunday</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            <ul>
              
              <li>Wake up early and catch the mesmerizing sunrise</li>
              <li>Return to campsite, freshen up, and breakfast</li>
              <li>Try out Longest Zipline Adventure ( Self-sponsored – Approx Rs 250 – Rs 400 )</li>
              <li>Self-sponsored lunch en-route</li>
              <li>Reach Bangalore by 10:00 PM ( approx )</li>
              
            </ul>
            <br>
          </p>

            
